{"tid":992370,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"安祖蓮娜祖莉養子才 15 歲就已經長到 170！一身帥氣西裝陪媽媽走紅毯超有明星架式！","createTime":"2019-01-23T06:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T16:51:03.000Z","uid":9573,"like":11,"dislike":428,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"6f46d72c0606600388985e4687d02f7dfd5d592e","tid":992370,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:20:12.000Z","msg":"原本好萊塢令人稱羨的金童玉女、布萊德彼特（Brad Pitt）和安潔莉娜裘莉（Angelina Jolie），離婚後因為 6 名小孩的撫養權鬧得不愉快，不過在官司未明朗之前，裘莉依舊帶著小孩們趴趴走，其中除了 17 歲領養的柬埔寨男孩梅鐸斯芝萬裘莉-彼特（Maddox Chivan Jolie Pitt）之外，越南籍養子帕克斯裘莉彼特（Pax Jolie Pitt）也已經 15 歲，開始跟著母親參加各種活動，有稜有角的臉龐和風格讓人直呼超有型！<br />\n<br />\n▼布萊德彼特（Brad Pitt）和安潔莉娜裘莉（Angelina Jolie） 6 名子女先前全家一出動就是話題，大陣仗往往引來媒體拍攝，隨著兩人離婚小孩們的歸屬也成為討論話題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86815/5c453054b69cb.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86815%2F5c453054b69cb.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=dc8629f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86815/5c453054c8c09.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86815%2F5c453054c8c09.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=02c03b97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86815/5c45305504c3f.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86815%2F5c45305504c3f.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=26ffb7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼17 歲的柬埔寨男孩梅鐸斯芝萬裘莉-彼特愈來愈有型、12 歲的大女兒夏蘿（Shiloh Nouvel Jolie-Pitt）充滿個性的打扮皆相當受到關注。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86815/5c45313d6a770.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86815%2F5c45313d6a770.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=4f64fb58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86815/5c45313e82356.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86815%2F5c45313e82356.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=2b01e0e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86815/5c45313fefcb3.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86815%2F5c45313fefcb3.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=550cb0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86815/5c45324bd53e5.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86815%2F5c45324bd53e5.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=a39fb180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼最近 15 歲的越南籍養子帕克斯裘莉彼特（Pax Jolie Pitt）也多次被媒體捕捉，日前更隨著媽媽安潔莉娜裘莉一同參加金球獎走紅毯，相當具有明星氣勢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86815/5c4530cdbb424.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86815%2F5c4530cdbb424.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=3e909158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86815/5c4530ccf2858.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86815%2F5c4530ccf2858.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=8bcf032d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86815/5c4530ce79900.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86815%2F5c4530ce79900.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=f73174cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86815/5c4532fa63d12.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt